      "full_name": "Iskra Engineering Design Bureau JSC named after I.I. Kartukov",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Iskra Engineering Design Bureau JSC named after I.I. Kartukov is one of the leading producers of solid-fuelled rocket motors. The company has developed various solid-propellant gas generators used in the mechanisms for deploying missile elements, emergency landing gear release and rapid start of turbojet engines. Since its foundation, the company has developed and delivered for supply more than 200 solidpropellant engines for anti-aircraft, tactical, aviation, naval and space missile systems for the Russian Ministry of Defence. Moreover, the company also ensures its compliance with the requirements for licensing in the field of weapons and military equipment and for obtaining a state defence order.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}